					<li>Financials submitted</li>
					<li>Executive interview</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="full three">
			<div class="content">
				<ul class="paw">
					<h4>Step 3:<br> Discovery Day</h4>
					<li>Spend the day at Woof Gang Bakery HQ in Orlando, Florida</li>
					<li>Understand what your responsibilities are as a franchisee</li>
					<li>Meeting and interacting with staff who will train and support your franchise</li>
					<li>A full understanding of the Woof Gang Bakery brand and culture</li>
					<li>Receive and review Franchise Disclosure Documents</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="full four">
			<div class="content">
				<ul class="paw">
					<h4>Step 4:<br> Final Steps</h4>
					<li>Franchise agreement signed</li>
					<li>Site approved and lease signed</li>
					<li>Financing secured</li>
					<li>Training completed</li>
					<li>Open your store</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

